"to declare a test to be skipped under certain conditions like mismatching "
"platforms or dependencies. Similarly, use the ``# doctest: +SKIP`` directive "
"(see `doctest.SKIP <https://docs.python.org/3/library/doctest.html#doctest."
"SKIP>`_) to skip a doctest statically."
