"to use the auto-generated id."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.8/site-packages/_pytest/python.py:docstring
#: of _pytest.python.Metafunc.parametrize:37
msgid ""
"If it is a callable it will be called for each entry in ``argvalues``, and "
"the return value is used as part of the auto-generated id for the whole set "
"(where parts are joined with dashes (\"-\")). This is useful to provide more "
"specific ids for certain items, e.g. dates.  Returning ``None`` will use an "
"auto-generated id."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.8/site-packages/_pytest/python.py:docstring
#: of _pytest.python.Metafunc.parametrize:44
